intro:
DEF CON Group in New Jersey! Dirty Jersey Represent! We meet at Sub Culture, Jersey City once a month to work on hardware/software projects!

CFP: info (at) defcon201 [dot] org

ClearNet: https://www.defcon201.org

post.body:
Welcome to DEFCON 201's ZeroMe! #DEFCON201 is the North East New Jersey DEFCON Groups (www.defcongroups.org) Chapter. We meet at WHEALTH Cafe once a month to hack on technology projects!

ClearNet: https://www.defcon201.org

ZeroNet: http://127.0.0.1:43110/defcon201.bit

ATTENTION: #35c3 in Germany is going on RIGHT NOW throughout the weekend! Catch LiveStreams (https://streaming.media.ccc.de/35c3/ ), Scheduel (https://fahrplan.events.ccc.de/ ), Archive (https://www.youtube.com/user/mediacccde ) and IRC (http://irc.hackint.org ) & TorIRC (http://5ogdsfyoqk47ompu.onion)
